<h1 id='api-query'>API Query</h1>
<p>Querying DB via HTTP Endpoints is really easy and follows a simple key value pair standard.</p>

<aside class="notice">
You must know the field names of the collection to query before building a query
</aside>

<aside class="warning">API Query Builder is only applicable to Platform Endpoints</aside>

<p>Example:</p>

<p>Consider a collection name <strong>TASK</strong></p>

<p>It has following fields :</p>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Fields</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>name</td>
<td>text</td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>amount</td>
<td>number</td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>created_on</td>
<td>datetime</td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>manager</td>
<td>reference</td>
<td></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id='text-queries'>Text Queries</h2><h3 id='query-on-single-field'>Query on single field</h3>
<p><code>oquery=name=Dave Smith</code></p>
<h3 id='query-on-multiple-fields'>Query on multiple fields</h3>
<p><code>oquery=name=Dave Smith,amount=0</code></p>
<h3 id='starts-with-query'>Starts With Query</h3>
<p><code>oquery=name==Dave Smith</code></p>

<aside class="notice">
Notice the double equal after the name
</aside>
<h3 id='does-not-starts-with-query'>Does Not Starts with Query</h3>
<p><code>oquery=name=!=Dave</code></p>
<h3 id='contains-query'>Contains Query</h3>
<p><code>oquery=name=*Dave</code></p>
<h3 id='does-not-contain-query'>Does Not Contain Query</h3>
<p><code>oquery=name=!*Dave</code></p>
<h2 id='number-queries'>Number Queries</h2><h3 id='equals-than'>Equals Than</h3>
<p><code>oquery=amount===0</code></p>
<h3 id='greater-than'>Greater Than</h3>
<p><code>oquery=amount=&gt;0</code></p>
<h3 id='less-than'>Less Than</h3>
<p><code>oquery=amount=&lt;0</code></p>
<h2 id='date-queries'>Date Queries</h2><h3 id='today'>Today</h3>
<p><code>oquery=created_on=today</code></p>
<h3 id='yesterday'>Yesterday</h3>
<p><code>oquery=created_on=yesterday</code></p>
<h3 id='day-before-yesterday'>Day Before Yesterday</h3>
<p><code>oquery=created_on=daybeforeyesterday</code></p>
<h3 id='custom'>Custom</h3>
<p><code>oquery=created_on=#in2018-07</code></p>

<p><code>oquery=created_on=on2018-07-15</code></p>
